data.description: No need in looking any further, 507 Shelmore Lane in Moss Creek is everything you'll need and more!Enjoy entertaining, yet having the kitchen close by, take a step out back and take advantage of the spacious fenced in back yard with a storage shed, plenty of space for any occasion or just a peaceful night by a fire... Upstairs is perfect, a loft area centrally located near the guest bathroom and bedrooms. As you travel through the master bedroom you'll notice plenty of closet space and as you pass through the master bath you find yourself in a spacious walk in closet!Don't delay schedule your showing today!
